{"tid":2498140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眾新聞: 打完2針大陸國藥疫苗，“回港易”內地返港港人隔離檢疫期間確診！","createTime":"2021-04-21T03:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T03:42:37.000Z","uid":319512,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d84accdd2db2028f8ee5b2ac35cfc351d41f5bed","tid":2498140,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeUEUwu81xTJ31ChDAmBm41ZEf99eqrWBrnocAg8kcKRg?filename=jphgAPN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjphgAPN.jpg&h=d92cf994&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30b3ad1a30697c0ee7e464fd60968724d8d800d8","tid":2498140,"uid":183090,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:21:48.000Z","msg":"計本地感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9df379511bed638778120660789b1495315898","tid":2498140,"uid":319512,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d84accdd2db2028f8ee5b2ac35cfc351d41f5bed","tid":2498140,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jphgAPN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjphgAPN.jpg&h=d92cf994&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"眾新聞接獲消息，一名56歲香港女子，報稱上月19日在福建接種第二劑疫苗，18天後即本月6日從福建回港，之後在港接受14天檢疫期間，今日正式確診。據了解，該名女子接種的是國藥疫苗，國藥集團稱疫苗的有效率保護率為79.34%。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心在記者會簡介個案詳情時，未有主動交代確診個案有否接種疫苗，衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君僅表示，該名56歲女子4月6日從福建搭高鐵，經深圳灣回港，女子住荃灣芙蓉大廈的劏房，正接受家居隔離。她於隔離期間第12天的樣本經病毒測試發現結果呈陽性，今日確診，現階段未能分類為本地或輸入個案。<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞記者問到個案是否接種疫苗後，衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君始證實，該女子分別在2月19日和3月19日接種疫苗，但不知道疫苗牌子。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料國藥集團官方聲明，疫苗的有效率保護率為79.34%。國藥疫苗目前仍未獲世界認可列入「緊急使用清單」，但於去年12月首次在海外獲批緊急使用。而國家衛健委資料顯示，滅活疫苗需要接種兩劑；建議兩劑相隔時間為至少3週，不多於8週，在接種第二劑大約14天後，接種者可以產生較好的免疫效果。<br />\n<br />\n另外，一名46歲女子4月6日透過「回港易」從東莞回港，同樣今日正式確診。張竹君表示，在香港逗留時間較長，相信較大機會是本地感染。患者4月10至19日在如心酒店當房務員，又到過屯門三聖邨廣東名門海鮮酒家、荃灣嘉記燒味。張竹君又指，雖然兩宗個案均於4月6日經深圳灣返港，但時間相距約3小時，相信無接觸。"},{"pid":"e0fc5560b7516663731ad65e47777274c7144f83","tid":2498140,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d84accdd2db2028f8ee5b2ac35cfc351d41f5bed","tid":2498140,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jphgAPN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjphgAPN.jpg&h=d92cf994&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:22:38.000Z","msg":"Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1431924490484289/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F366243453719070%2Fposts%2F1431924490484289%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=9466f38f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/366243453719070/posts/1431924490484289/</a>"},{"pid":"1cac91b03fa3598d7730f9f92cb73fbd90f89d04","tid":2498140,"uid":319512,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"30b3ad1a30697c0ee7e464fd60968724d8d800d8","tid":2498140,"uid":183090,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:21:48.000Z","msg":"計本地感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:22:59.000Z","msg":"隔離檢疫都計本地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa17c3ba02bbf690a48d86253e04d6b43bee5fe","tid":2498140,"uid":319512,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d84accdd2db2028f8ee5b2ac35cfc351d41f5bed","tid":2498140,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jphgAPN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjphgAPN.jpg&h=d92cf994&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:23:44.000Z","msg":"大陸針，打左18日都會中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下專家點樣兜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" 